included.description:
Working with Zamen International, an NPO based in Michigan helping women and children. The goal is to improve their donation process and increase donation volume.
Conducted thorough stakeholder interviews with staff, service providers and website design team to better understand the scope and scenarios;
Conducted survey and in-depth user interviews to understand donation behavior, motivation, and gap. 
Produced wireframes and formed recommendations.
